snippet.title: New Character Demo - "Kaedehara Kazuha: Wandering Winds" | Genshin Impact
snippet.description:
The clouds float above the vast mountains, the sky is azure and the water is still. It's a beautiful day to create poetry.
It's a pity that there are always people who don't appreciate the beauty of literature...
But it matters naught. When the wind of the sword settles, the fallen leaves will drift through the wind and the poems will come to life again.

Download FREE: https://genshin.mihoyo.com/en
